# ğŸš— License Plate Detection & Recognition (Web App)

A **real-time License Plate Detection and Recognition system** built using **Streamlit**, **YOLO**, and **OCR**.
The application supports **live webcam feed** and **uploaded video files**, detects **only license plates**, highlights **high-confidence detections**, and displays recognized plate numbers in a **live-updating table alongside the video**.

---

## âœ¨ Key Features

* ğŸ¥ Live **Webcam License Plate Detection**
