* ğŸ¯ **License Plateâ€“Only Detection** (No vehicle detection)
* ğŸ”² **Bounding Boxes for High-Confidence Plates Only**
* ğŸ”¤ **Improved OCR Accuracy**

  * Uppercase output
  * Reduced duplicate text
* ğŸ“Š **Real-Time Detection Table**

  * License plate number
  * Confidence score
* âš¡ Real-time processing
* ğŸ¨ Simple and clean UI

