## ğŸ–¥ï¸ How the App Works

### Webcam Mode

1. Select **Webcam**
2. Allow camera access
3. License plates are detected in real time
4. Detected plates appear instantly in the table

### Video Upload Mode

1. Upload a video file
2. Video starts playing immediately
3. License plates are detected while the video plays
4. Results update live in the table

---

## ğŸ“Š Detection Table Details

| Column       | Description                       |
| ------------ | --------------------------------- |
| Plate Number | OCR-recognized license plate text |
| Confidence   | Detection confidence score        |

Only **high-confidence detections** are shown and highlighted in the video.

---

## ğŸ”§ OCR Processing Notes

* OCR output is converted to **UPPERCASE**
* Repeated detections are filtered
* Low-confidence OCR results are ignored

